    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-12-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-12-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="1165"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1165">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/55.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Ambassador to Spain</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 13, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your December 12. Instructions were sent yesterday to American Consul at
                    Chihuahua to make proper representations to Villa. Department is today sending
                    special consular representative<note n="1" xml:id="d1165fn1">Mr.
                        Carothers.</note> who has favorable acquaintance with Villa to reinforce
                    representations Consul at Chihuahua is expected to make.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
